schools.name: C. C. Mason Elementary School (Col. Charles Clayborn)

data.description: Fantastic opportunity to own coveted views of the hill country and lake travis that don't come to market very often. Beautifully unique home that includes a full second kitchen on the second level, perfect for a mother in law suite, tenant, airbnb etc. The expansive lot is large enough to build an ADU/ guest house and easily add a pool. No city taxes and no airbnb restrictions. Secluded but only about 10 minutes to the Cedar Park city center. Enjoy your coffee on the wrap around porch and sunset views every evening. Neighborhood has its own private lake access and boat ramp. This is the home for you if you’re looking for privacy!
